    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works of art or architecture that are depicted in another work of art. Examples would be a painting depicted in a reproductive print or an architectural work depicted in a drawing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
